00:27:36.240 --> 00:27:39.124
It means some justice

00:27:39.480 --> 00:27:41.630
for the Cuban people

00:27:41.640 --> 00:27:45.190
for 67 years. Sorry, we have been

00:27:45.200 --> 00:27:46.430
ignored

00:27:46.440 --> 00:27:49.270
by everybody: the United

00:27:49.270 --> 00:27:49.280
