downfall

00:27:59.840 --> 00:28:01.750
of the Castro regime.

00:28:01.750 --> 00:28:01.760
Sorry,

00:28:01.760 --> 00:28:02.710
I'm

00:28:02.710 --> 00:28:02.720
a

00:28:02.720 --> 00:28:04.014
little emotional.

