And

00:28:06.040 --> 00:28:07.750
we're ready to go back

00:28:07.760 --> 00:28:10.670
and help in the reconstruction

00:28:10.680 --> 00:28:13.030
of our country

00:28:13.040 --> 00:28:15.190
with work, with money, with

00:28:15.200 --> 00:28:17.230
investment,

00:28:17.240 --> 00:28:20.070
and

00:28:20.080 --> 00:28:23.430
with love

00:28:23.440 --> 00:28:24.310
that has been lacking in

00:28:24.320 --> 00:28:28.870
Cuba for the last six decades.

00:28:28.880 --> 00:28:30.110
Oscar, thank you so much for sharing

00:28:30.120 --> 00:28:31.470
your perspective. I know you're getting

00:28:31.480 --> 00:28:33.230
emotional because this is a huge day for

00:28:33.240 --> 00:28:40.590
the Cuban community.

00:28:40.600 --> 00:28:42.430
It blessed me

00:28:42.440 --> 00:28:52.910
because I appreciate it.

00:28:52.910 --> 00:28:52.920
Yeah,

00:28:52.920 --> 00:28:54.630
met with them recently. The CIA director

00:28:54.640 --> 00:28:55.950
was down there a few weeks ago. There's

00:28:55.960 --> 00:28:57.790
some State Department communications

00:28:57.800 --> 00:29:00.830
that occur. I just don't see a lot of

00:29:00.840 --> 00:29:01.870
At the end of the day, they got to make

00:29:01.880 --> 00:29:03.870
a decision. Their system doesn't work.

00:29:03.880 --> 00:29:05.590
Their economic system does not

00:29:05.600 --> 00:29:08.110
work. It's broken. And you can't fix it

00:29:08.120 --> 00:29:09.550
with the current political system that's

00:29:09.560 --> 00:29:11.310
in place. They just don't comprehend how

00:29:11.320 --> 00:29:13.670
to do it. And it's a failed state. Like

00:29:13.680 --> 00:29:14.950
their economy and the model they're

00:29:14.960 --> 00:29:16.150
trying to follow in Cuba doesn't

00:29:16.160 --> 00:29:17.550
resemble what anyone is doing anywhere

00:29:17.560 --> 00:29:19.510
in the world. I mean,

00:29:19.520 --> 00:29:20.870
there are other ways to do it that can

00:29:20.880 --> 00:29:22.510
provide the people of Cuba prosperity

00:29:22.520 --> 00:29:24.270
and opportunity. And it's what I said in

00:29:24.280 --> 00:29:25.950
the video to them the other day.

00:29:25.960 --> 00:29:27.550
You look at Cuba, the Bahamas,

00:29:27.560 --> 00:29:29.630
Jamaica, the Dominican Republic, and here

00:29:29.640 --> 00:29:31.990
in Florida. Cuba's surrounded by places

00:29:32.000 --> 00:29:33.350
where people have the right to do things

00:29:33.360 --> 00:29:35.350
like own a business, work for

00:29:35.360 --> 00:29:36.710
themselves,

00:29:36.720 --> 00:29:38.310
and be able to vote for the

00:29:38.320 --> 00:29:40.830
leaders that govern them or replace

00:29:40.840 --> 00:29:42.750
them. So, if that's possible all around

00:29:42.760 --> 00:29:44.670
Cuba, why is that

00:29:44.680 --> 00:29:46.870
not possible inside of Cuba? And right

00:29:46.880 --> 00:29:47.950
now there just doesn't seem to be

00:29:47.960 --> 00:29:49.990
people over there in charge of the

00:29:50.000 --> 00:29:51.950
regime who are in any way open to any of

00:29:51.960 --> 00:29:53.590
those changes. And the things they've

00:29:53.590 --> 00:29:53.600
talked

00:29:53.600 --> 00:29:55.270
about economically are cosmetic in

00:29:55.280 --> 00:29:57.070
nature. They're not real because that's

00:29:57.080 --> 00:29:58.230
what they've gotten used to all these

00:29:58.240 --> 00:30:00.110
years is just buying time and waiting us

00:30:00.120 --> 00:30:01.270
out. They're not going to be able to

00:30:01.280 --> 00:30:02.870
wait us out or buy time. We're very

00:30:02.880 --> 00:30:04.710
serious. We're very focused.

00:30:04.720 --> 00:30:05.990
As I told you a moment ago in the

00:30:06.000 --> 00:30:08.070
context of Iran, the president's

00:30:08.080 --> 00:30:10.150
preference is always a negotiated

00:30:10.160 --> 00:30:11.750
agreement that's peaceful. That's always

00:30:11.760 --> 00:30:13.110
our preference. That remains our

00:30:13.120 --> 00:30:14.710
preference with Cuba. I'm just being

00:30:14.720 --> 00:30:16.590
honest with you. You know, the likelihood of that

00:30:16.600 --> 00:30:18.470
happening given who we're dealing with

00:30:18.480 --> 00:30:20.710
right now is not high. But if they have

00:30:20.720 --> 00:30:22.390
a change of heart, we're here,

00:30:22.400 --> 00:30:23.470
and in the meantime, we'll keep doing

00:30:23.480 --> 00:30:24.110
what we need to do.

00:30:24.120 --> 00:30:25.750
It sounds a lot like nation building.

00:30:25.760 --> 00:30:27.110
The administration doesn't believe

00:30:27.120 --> 00:30:28.350
in using force

00:30:28.350 --> 00:30:28.360
for

00:30:28.360 --> 00:30:29.630
nation building. It's not nation

00:30:29.640 --> 00:30:31.310
building.

00:30:31.320 --> 00:30:32.430
We are addressing something that's

00:30:32.440 --> 00:30:33.630
directly related to the national

00:30:33.640 --> 00:30:34.950
security of the United States. We are

00:30:34.960 --> 00:30:36.390
involved in places all over the world.

00:30:36.400 --> 00:30:38.790
You're asking me about Ebola. Important,

00:30:38.800 --> 00:30:40.830
but Ebola is in Africa. Cuba's 90 miles

00:30:40.840 --> 00:30:42.830
from our shores. So if you have a

00:30:42.840 --> 00:30:44.550
systemic meltdown in that country, which

00:30:44.560 --> 00:30:45.990
is where they're headed, their power

00:30:46.000 --> 00:30:47.510
plants, by the way,

00:30:47.520 --> 00:30:49.510
the reason why their power plants break

00:30:49.520 --> 00:30:51.110
down, they've been having blackouts for

00:30:51.120 --> 00:30:53.110
years. They had major blackouts last

00:30:53.120 --> 00:30:54.590
year, and they were still getting free

00:30:54.600 --> 00:30:56.510
Venezuelan oil. They haven't spent a

00:30:56.520 --> 00:30:59.870
penny in fixing their energy production

00:30:59.870 --> 00:30:59.880
or

00:30:59.880 --> 00:31:01.470
their electrical grid. They don't

00:31:01.480 --> 00:31:02.670
spend any money on that stuff; they

00:31:02.680 --> 00:31:03.830
pocket it.

00:31:03.840 --> 00:31:05.590
They have a private military company

00:31:05.600 --> 00:31:08.390
named GAESA who's sitting on $18 billion

00:31:08.400 --> 00:31:10.550
of assets, and not a penny of

00:31:10.560 --> 00:31:12.350
that transfers over to the state budget.

00:31:12.360 --> 00:31:13.790
Not a penny of that goes over to help

00:31:13.800 --> 00:31:16.870
the people of Cuba—not one cent. So

00:31:16.880 --> 00:31:18.670
even if they had all the diesel in the

00:31:18.680 --> 00:31:19.670
world, they still wouldn't be able to

00:31:19.680 --> 00:31:21.350
generate energy because they've

00:31:21.360 --> 00:31:23.030
stolen the money and haven't invested in

00:31:23.040 --> 00:31:24.510
their energy infrastructure. So you're

00:31:24.510 --> 00:31:24.520
heading

00:31:24.520 --> 00:31:25.870
for a failed state. That's what

00:31:25.880 --> 00:31:27.590
you have now. But it's 90 miles from our

00:31:27.600 --> 00:31:29.510
shores, so we'll be impacted by the

00:31:29.520 --> 00:31:31.430
migratory crisis, by any violence and

00:31:31.440 --> 00:31:33.070
instability that happens there.

00:31:33.080 --> 00:31:35.510
It directly implicates the United

00:31:35.510 --> 00:31:35.520
States'national

00:31:35.520 --> 00:31:37.910
interest. So the future

00:31:37.920 --> 00:31:39.630
of Cuba belongs to the people of Cuba in

00:31:39.640 --> 00:31:40.750
terms of how they're governed, what the

00:31:40.760 --> 00:31:42.870
system looks like, and so forth. But

00:31:42.880 --> 00:31:44.510
the national security threat

00:31:44.510 --> 00:31:44.520
is

00:31:44.520 --> 00:31:46.430
100% something we're going to focus on

00:31:46.440 --> 00:31:50.310
because that's about America.

00:31:50.320 --> 00:31:51.910
I loved it.

00:31:51.920 --> 00:31:53.350
Praise the Lord.

00:31:53.360 --> 00:31:55.270
It's time

00:31:57.200 --> 00:31:59.270
for the Cuban people to have a major

00:31:59.280 --> 00:32:00.630
revival.

00:32:00.640 --> 00:32:03.710
And as I saw in this, I saw that

00:32:03.720 --> 00:32:04.990
leader

00:32:07.040 --> 00:32:09.590
sacrificing chickens and drinking the

00:32:09.600 --> 00:32:12.350
