00:32:12.350 --> 00:32:12.360
what

00:32:12.360 --> 00:32:14.390
looked like a cellar below this

00:32:14.400 --> 00:32:16.430
house. It was a beautiful white house

00:32:16.440 --> 00:32:17.430
with a

00:32:17.440 --> 00:32:18.790
red

00:32:18.800 --> 00:32:22.990
