00:32:23.000 --> 00:32:24.350
killing these chickens and looking at

00:32:24.360 --> 00:32:26.430
President Trump's picture.

00:32:26.440 --> 00:32:29.190
And as he was doing this—and I don't

00:32:29.200 --> 00:32:31.790
focus on the

00:32:31.790 --> 00:32:31.800
darkness—I

00:32:31.800 --> 00:32:34.670
saw him start to shapeshift into a

00:32:34.680 --> 00:32:37.470
dog, his face,

00:32:37.480 --> 00:32:39.990
but I saw a man in the corner who had

00:32:40.000 --> 00:32:42.510
antlers on his head, doing some kind of

00:32:42.520 --> 00:32:44.430
dance with his shirt off,

00:32:44.440 --> 00:32:45.910
and they were doing satanic stuff

00:32:45.920 --> 00:32:47.950
against our president. And the Lord

00:32:47.960 --> 00:32:51.150
said,

00:32:51.160 --> 00:32:52.270
'Intercede.'And

00:32:52.280 --> 00:32:56.230
I saw they had a lead case

00:32:56.240 --> 00:32:58.550
with a device that could not be

00:32:58.560 --> 00:33:01.230
sniffed out by our sniffers that was

00:33:01.240 --> 00:33:03.350
given to them by the Russian government

00:33:03.360 --> 00:33:05.830
from the 1960s

00:33:05.840 --> 00:33:08.670
Cuban Missile Crisis.

00:33:08.680 --> 00:33:11.070
They have weapons that we don't know they

00:33:11.080 --> 00:33:14.310
have. But as I saw this, he was

00:33:14.320 --> 00:33:16.710
going to set this thing off

00:33:16.720 --> 00:33:19.910
trying to retaliate from America coming

00:33:19.920 --> 00:33:22.310
within to make it uninhabitable on this

00:33:22.320 --> 00:33:24.470
mountain. There was a mountain there,

00:33:24.480 --> 00:33:26.350
and they had a base in this mountain,

00:33:26.360 --> 00:33:29.950
and there were gold coins and gold bars

00:33:29.960 --> 00:33:32.310
all inside of this mountain

00:33:32.320 --> 00:33:35.190
and $100 bills,

00:33:35.200 --> 00:33:37.150
and they put it on a boat.

00:33:37.160 --> 00:33:39.190
He didn't fly out. He went to the

00:33:39.200 --> 00:33:41.830
Dominican Republic

00:33:41.840 --> 00:33:44.950
through a system in Cuba

00:33:44.960 --> 00:33:46.550
to get away. And he got in a boat and

00:33:46.560 --> 00:33:47.870
Claudia

00:33:47.880 --> 00:33:50.470
kept

00:33:50.470 --> 00:33:50.480
him—Claudia

00:33:50.480 --> 00:33:54.270
kept him in Mexico at a resort,

00:33:54.280 --> 00:33:56.830
hiding the leader of Cuba. In the days

00:33:56.840 --> 00:33:57.910
ahead,

00:33:57.920 --> 00:33:59.710
he goes to

00:34:02.470 --> 00:34:02.480
the

00:34:03.240 --> 00:34:05.270
Dominican Republic and flies out in a

00:34:05.280 --> 00:34:07.510
private jet.

00:34:07.520 --> 00:34:09.629
He didn't fly out of Cuba.

00:34:09.639 --> 00:34:11.430
He took a boat,

00:34:11.440 --> 00:34:14.470
and it's 400 miles away to the Dominican

00:34:14.480 --> 00:34:17.070
Republic from what I understand from the

00:34:17.080 --> 00:34:21.190
point of Cuba where I saw him leaving.

00:34:21.200 --> 00:34:24.470
So, this is the kind of stuff I saw.

00:34:24.480 --> 00:34:27.470
And I saw when it comes to the CIA, I

00:34:27.480 --> 00:34:29.270
saw projects

00:34:29.280 --> 00:34:31.070
that were dark,

00:34:31.080 --> 00:34:35.110
that were

00:34:35.120 --> 00:34:38.149
worse than waterboarding in these rooms.

00:34:38.159 --> 00:34:40.990
I saw things that were very dark.

00:34:41.000 --> 00:34:42.830
But the Lord said he was exposing

00:34:42.840 --> 00:34:45.110
things,

00:34:45.120 --> 00:34:48.629
and I saw finances coming

00:34:48.639 --> 00:34:52.350
to Cuba from America with investments.

00:34:52.360 --> 00:34:54.750
But the Lord said, 'Pay attention to

00:34:54.760 --> 00:34:59.310
Cuba. Don't underestimate your

00:34:59.310 --> 00:34:59.320
enemy.'How

00:34:59.320 --> 00:35:01.510
many times the Lord said that? 'Don't

00:35:01.520 --> 00:35:05.390
underestimate your enemy. Watch Cuba.

00:35:05.400 --> 00:35:07.350
Watch Cuba.'And I've had video after

00:35:07.360 --> 00:35:09.510
video; the Lord said, 'Watch

00:35:09.510 --> 00:35:09.520
Cuba.'The

00:35:09.520 --> 00:35:12.430
mules,

00:35:12.440 --> 00:35:16.590
the

00:35:16.590 --> 00:35:16.600
balseros.

00:35:16.600 --> 00:35:20.110
Don't underestimate your

00:35:20.120 --> 00:35:23.070
enemy. The Lord said they're cocky;

00:35:23.080 --> 00:35:24.350
'We're going to do this, we're going to

00:35:24.360 --> 00:35:25.870
do that.'But I say they have a

00:35:25.880 --> 00:35:30.230
stronghold of people with blue uniforms

00:35:30.230 --> 00:35:30.240
that

00:35:30.240 --> 00:35:32.630
are the resistance

00:35:32.640 --> 00:35:36.150
to this because they're loyal to the

00:35:36.160 --> 00:35:37.870
Castros

00:35:37.880 --> 00:35:39.830
and to the leader there now.

00:35:39.840 --> 00:35:43.670
And I saw a loyalty that I was

00:35:43.670 --> 00:35:43.680
praying,

00:35:43.680 --> 00:35:46.390
'Lay down your arms.'But I saw gang

00:35:46.400 --> 00:35:48.950
leaders like

00:35:48.960 --> 00:35:51.830
MS-13 gang leaders—that's the

00:35:51.830 --> 00:35:51.840
only way

00:35:51.840 --> 00:35:53.190
to tell, I don't know how else to

00:35:53.200 --> 00:35:57.910
say it—in Cuba that were like drug lords

00:35:57.920 --> 00:35:59.830
for prostitution,

00:35:59.840 --> 00:36:02.430
drug trafficking, and such coming out of

00:36:02.440 --> 00:36:05.590
Cuba

00:36:05.590 --> 00:36:05.600
that

00:36:05.600 --> 00:36:08.150
was connected to Colombia and

00:36:08.160 --> 00:36:10.070
Venezuela.

00:36:10.080 --> 00:36:12.630
They were like bosses,

00:36:12.640 --> 00:36:16.190
but I saw a free Cuba coming.

00:36:16.200 --> 00:36:19.390
But there were our men and women of service that we pray over

00:36:19.390 --> 00:36:19.400
who

00:36:19.400 --> 00:36:22.030
would go

00:36:22.040 --> 00:36:25.070
in in the middle of the night and invade

00:36:25.080 --> 00:36:28.510
with tech like I've never seen. I saw it

00:36:28.520 --> 00:36:30.630
go dark

00:36:30.640 --> 00:36:34.550
with cyber warfare

00:36:34.560 --> 00:36:35.990
to

00:36:36.000 --> 00:36:39.190
be able to infiltrate

00:36:39.190 --> 00:36:39.200
and

00:36:39.200 --> 00:36:42.630
take over more easily. But

00:36:42.640 --> 00:36:46.990
he was in a bunker in the mountain.

00:36:47.000 --> 00:36:49.150
He was in a bunker, and there was one way

00:36:49.160 --> 00:36:51.590
in and there was a secret way out, and I

00:36:51.600 --> 00:36:52.910
saw they couldn't get out with a

00:36:52.920 --> 00:37:01.510
helicopter.

00:37:01.520 --> 00:37:02.710
So,

00:37:03.960 --> 00:37:05.310
those are the things we've been praying

00:37:05.320 --> 00:37:07.390
over for quite a while and now we see

00:37:07.400 --> 00:37:09.510
this stuff in the news today.

00:37:09.520 --> 00:37:12.990
It hasn't happened yet, but

00:37:13.000 --> 00:37:15.070
we see the birthing pains of it. So,

00:37:15.080 --> 00:37:17.950
it's pretty accurate so far.

00:37:17.960 --> 00:37:19.830
To the people who don't believe in

00:37:19.840 --> 00:37:21.950
it, you don't have to watch.

00:37:21.960 --> 00:37:25.030
But I'm telling you, a great revival, I

00:37:25.040 --> 00:37:27.750
believe, is coming to Cuba

00:37:27.760 --> 00:37:29.990
and a great shaking to awaken.

00:37:33.120 --> 00:37:35.270
And I believe with all my heart, it's

00:37:35.280 --> 00:37:36.790
sooner than later.

00:37:36.800 --> 00:37:37.830
Why?

00:37:37.840 --> 00:37:39.550
Because we're looking at the end of the

00:37:39.560 --> 00:37:41.750
end. And God said, 'I want the Cuban people

00:37:41.760 --> 00:37:44.990
to have a major

00:37:44.990 --> 00:37:45.000
revival.'So

00:37:45.000 --> 00:37:47.070
when the day happens, you'll

00:37:47.080 --> 00:37:48.430
remember

00:37:48.440 --> 00:37:50.550
the Lord said it.

00:37:50.560 --> 00:37:52.670
The Lord said it, not Brandon.

00:37:52.680 --> 00:37:55.710
We always attract to deflect;

00:37:55.720 --> 00:37:58.150
it's always about giving glory to Jesus.

00:37:58.160 --> 00:38:01.270
The same with Israel striking Iran. I

00:38:01.280 --> 00:38:04.070
said in the days ahead, I did not see

00:38:04.080 --> 00:38:08.390
America striking Iran anymore.

00:38:08.400 --> 00:38:09.990
I saw

00:38:10.000 --> 00:38:13.150
Israel doing it and people get very mad

00:38:13.160 --> 00:38:15.310
at Israel for what they're about to do.

00:38:15.320 --> 00:38:19.430
America pulls back.

00:38:19.440 --> 00:38:21.990
I saw America pulling

00:38:22.000 --> 00:38:23.270
back

00:38:23.280 --> 00:38:25.590
and Israel going full force one time.

00:38:25.600 --> 00:38:27.110
Boom.

00:38:27.120 --> 00:38:29.470
With devices we've never seen used

00:38:29.480 --> 00:38:31.230
before.

00:38:31.240 --> 00:38:33.476
And it would be used on the mountain. And

00:38:33.486 --> 00:38:34.550
the mountain was glowing

00:38:34.560 --> 00:38:36.270
in the dark.

00:38:36.280 --> 00:38:38.070
It was glowing. Now, I know that's a

00:38:38.070 --> 00:38:38.080
metaphor—I

00:38:38.080 --> 00:38:39.350
don't think it really is

00:38:39.360 --> 00:38:41.550
glowing with green light—but I saw

00:38:41.560 --> 00:38:44.510
Israel about to use tech with some kind

00:38:44.520 --> 00:38:46.750
of device that has never been used

00:38:46.760 --> 00:38:48.910
before.

00:38:48.920 --> 00:38:50.350
And it made the mountain where you

00:38:50.360 --> 00:38:51.990
couldn't go in it to get this

00:38:52.000 --> 00:38:55.150
uranium.

00:38:55.160 --> 00:38:57.230
Okay?

00:38:57.240 --> 00:38:59.950
And I said, 'Watch, pray for

00:38:59.950 --> 00:38:59.960
Israel.'I

00:38:59.960 --> 00:39:03.830
saw an attack coming against Israel that

00:39:03.840 --> 00:39:05.710
was worse than the one that happened in

00:39:05.720 --> 00:39:07.030
October.

00:39:07.040 --> 00:39:10.630
It happens in the middle of the night.

00:39:10.640 --> 00:39:13.670
They use chemical weapons on the

00:39:13.680 --> 00:39:19.030
people this time with sprayers.

00:39:19.040 --> 00:39:21.190
It was a mustard-looking color. It was

00:39:21.200 --> 00:39:23.830
yellow.

00:39:23.840 --> 00:39:25.510
And they spray them and the trucks

00:39:25.520 --> 00:39:28.190
come out of the mountain

00:39:28.200 --> 00:39:30.110
and they're brought across

00:39:30.120 --> 00:39:32.830
Syria

00:39:32.840 --> 00:39:35.390
into Damascus,

00:39:35.400 --> 00:39:38.510
coming across Iraq at the top, and they

00:39:38.520 --> 00:39:41.790
brought it in a truck

00:39:41.800 --> 00:39:44.710
and they were 50-gallon drums

00:39:44.720 --> 00:39:47.230
and they gave it to, I believe it was

00:39:47.240 --> 00:39:50.350
like Hezbollah.

00:39:50.360 --> 00:39:52.550
So,

00:39:52.560 --> 00:39:54.030
those are the things we're praying over

00:39:54.030 --> 00:39:54.040
because

00:39:54.040 --> 00:39:56.710
I saw them trying to strike

00:39:56.720 --> 00:39:59.750
Israel,

00:39:59.760 --> 00:40:01.910
and so we continue to pray for

00:40:01.920 --> 00:40:03.070
Israel.

00:40:03.080 --> 00:40:04.590
We believe we have power and authority

00:40:04.600 --> 00:40:06.590
and we pray for the peace of Jerusalem.

00:40:06.600 --> 00:40:08.870
We pray for the peace of Israel.

00:40:08.880 --> 00:40:10.190
We pray for the covering over their

00:40:10.200 --> 00:40:14.190
people, their innocent people,

00:40:15.200 --> 00:40:17.830
and we pray that Iran is liberated. The

00:40:17.840 --> 00:40:20.390
Lord said, 'I'm bringing a great revival

00:40:20.400 --> 00:40:22.270
to Iran

00:40:22.280 --> 00:40:24.510
and I will shake Iran for the

00:40:24.520 --> 00:40:26.990
underground church will rise up and they

00:40:27.000 --> 00:40:29.630
will have a window.'And the Lord said,

00:40:29.640 --> 00:40:31.870
'Pray for the gray-headed man with the

00:40:31.880 --> 00:40:34.750
bald head, the prince, because they said

00:40:34.760 --> 00:40:36.510
in the days ahead, I saw him be

00:40:36.520 --> 00:40:39.870
assassinated.'And

00:40:39.880 --> 00:40:41.670
the Lord said, 'Pray

00:40:41.670 --> 00:40:41.680
for

00:40:44.670 --> 00:40:44.680
Reza

00:40:44.680 --> 00:40:49.110
Pahlavi.'I

00:40:49.120 --> 00:40:50.630
saw him being a leader there for a

00:40:50.640 --> 00:40:53.030
season, trying to speak out

00:40:53.040 --> 00:40:54.910
and do stuff, but then they took

00:40:54.920 --> 00:40:57.710
him out with a sniper.

00:40:57.720 --> 00:40:59.430
He was speaking

00:40:59.440 --> 00:41:02.550
and I saw a new leader

00:41:02.560 --> 00:41:04.430
coming up out of Iran. But when

00:41:04.440 --> 00:41:06.390
this happened, the Prince of Persia

00:41:06.400 --> 00:41:09.510
shrunk back for a season and I saw Iraq

00:41:09.520 --> 00:41:12.510
coming up and I saw blessing coming up

00:41:12.520 --> 00:41:18.270
out of Iraq.

00:41:18.280 --> 00:41:21.830
I know I go over these words a lot,

00:41:21.840 --> 00:41:23.150
but there's a lot of things the Lord

00:41:23.160 --> 00:41:26.750
gives us and it gets

00:41:26.760 --> 00:41:28.270
buried

00:41:28.280 --> 00:41:29.750
and people accuse you. 'Well, Brandon

00:41:29.750 --> 00:41:29.760
is

00:41:29.760 --> 00:41:31.030
buried. We don't know what you say

00:41:31.040 --> 00:41:33.190
all the time. You speak for three

00:41:33.190 --> 00:41:33.200
hours.'I

00:41:33.200 --> 00:41:34.870
don't want anybody to get lost in this. And I

00:41:34.870 --> 00:41:34.880
am

00:41:34.880 --> 00:41:36.790
not trying to hide

00:41:36.790 --> 00:41:36.800
anything.

00:41:36.800 --> 00:41:38.510
I try to bring everything out as much as

00:41:38.520 --> 00:41:40.790
I can remember to

00:41:40.800 --> 00:41:43.150
rehash it so you'll remember it, because I

00:41:43.160 --> 00:41:44.630
believe in my heart it will come to

00:41:44.640 --> 00:41:49.670
pass.

00:41:51.160 --> 00:41:52.270
So,

00:41:52.280 --> 00:41:54.190
here we are.

00:41:54.200 --> 00:41:56.830
Let's see what happens next.

00:41:56.840 --> 00:41:59.750
Praying over Taiwan for an invasion

00:41:59.760 --> 00:42:04.030
from China,

00:42:04.030 --> 00:42:04.040
with

00:42:04.040 --> 00:42:05.870
North Korea being a part of it.

00:42:05.880 --> 00:42:09.150
Praying over Ukraine

00:42:09.150 --> 00:42:09.160
and

00:42:09.160 --> 00:42:11.390
Russia.

00:42:11.400 --> 00:42:13.030
I'm curious about what happened

00:42:13.040 --> 00:42:14.790
with the meeting with him and

00:42:16.070 --> 00:42:16.080
Xi,

00:42:18.080 --> 00:42:22.670
and the

00:42:22.680 --> 00:42:25.030
big event they had this week.

00:42:27.400 --> 00:42:29.270
They had a cooking class together;

00:42:29.270 --> 00:42:29.280
I

00:42:29.280 --> 00:42:30.830
thought that was kind of fun.

00:42:30.840 --> 00:42:32.190
They did a cooking

00:42:32.200 --> 00:42:35.510
thing. Best friends that could hold hands.

00:42:35.520 --> 00:42:36.590
I thought, "Are they having a cooking

00:42:36.590 --> 00:42:36.600
party?

00:42:36.600 --> 00:42:38.230
They're making dumplings and

00:42:38.230 --> 00:42:38.240
stuff."Isn't

00:42:38.240 --> 00:42:39.590
that kind of interesting?

00:42:39.600 --> 00:42:41.430
Two men like that

00:42:41.440 --> 00:42:43.790
having a dumpling party,

00:42:43.800 --> 00:42:46.030
making some kind of crepes.

00:42:46.030 --> 00:42:46.040
I

00:42:46.040 --> 00:42:47.310
thought it was kind of funny. I

00:42:49.000 --> 00:42:50.150
guess it shows they like

00:42:50.160 --> 00:42:51.550
cooking,

00:42:51.560 --> 00:42:53.070
but whatever.

00:42:56.200 --> 00:43:02.670
Next,

00:43:02.680 --> 00:43:04.150
look, see, they even have a portrait

00:43:04.160 --> 00:43:05.310
together. They're all

00:43:05.320 --> 00:43:07.230
hanging together in a portrait. It's a

00:43:07.240 --> 00:43:09.670
painting.

00:43:09.680 --> 00:43:11.550
They're like best friends. I'm

00:43:11.560 --> 00:43:15.784
surprised they're not holding hands.

00:43:17.320 --> 00:43:21.830
Putin's excited about it.

00:43:21.840 --> 00:43:24.954
Best friends,

00:43:29.640 --> 00:43:31.670
I guess. Is Trump not invited?

00:43:31.680 --> 00:43:34.125
He didn't get to be in the picture.

00:43:41.200 --> 00:43:42.110
I wonder what Trump's thinking:

00:43:42.120 --> 00:43:45.150
"Well, you didn't make a picture of

00:43:45.150 --> 00:43:45.160
me."Look,

00:43:45.160 --> 00:43:46.390
they could put their flags

00:43:46.400 --> 00:43:48.390
together. Let's clap.

00:43:48.400 --> 00:43:51.710
2026, 2027—what's happening?

00:43:51.710 --> 00:43:51.720
Oh,

00:43:51.720 --> 00:43:54.910
shake hands.

00:43:54.920 --> 00:43:56.910
"You're my friend. See, we did more than

00:43:56.920 --> 00:43:59.015
Trump and you,

00:43:59.015 --> 00:43:59.025
right?"A

00:43:59.025 --> 00:44:02.710
hundred

00:44:02.710 --> 00:44:02.720
thousand

00:44:02.720 --> 00:44:06.510
Russians study Chinese, including

00:44:06.520 --> 00:44:10.510
20,000 in

00:44:10.510 --> 00:44:10.520
educational

00:44:10.520 --> 00:44:13.790
courses in China,

00:44:13.800 --> 00:44:15.950
right?

00:44:15.960 --> 00:44:17.470
Their kids are starting to learn Russian. So, they let

00:44:17.470 --> 00:44:17.480
him start

00:44:17.480 --> 00:44:18.630
Russian.

00:44:18.640 --> 00:44:20.190
They're going to shake hands.

00:44:20.200 --> 00:44:21.550
And then they did oil deals. I

00:44:21.560 --> 00:44:23.910
swear,

00:44:23.920 --> 00:44:25.470
didn't you hear President Trump say my

00:44:25.480 --> 00:44:27.190
party was better than his?

00:44:30.320 --> 00:44:31.750
What we do was better than

00:44:31.760 --> 00:44:33.075
theirs.

00:44:33.440 --> 00:44:35.830
I thought it was funny; I laughed.

00:44:35.840 --> 00:44:41.550
They're so competitive.

00:44:41.560 --> 00:44:43.270
Look, there they are again,

00:44:43.280 --> 00:44:45.430
shaking

00:44:45.440 --> 00:44:47.485
hands.

00:44:57.080 --> 00:44:59.590
Unity being shown.

00:45:09.920 --> 00:45:13.390
Now, this is interesting.

00:45:13.400 --> 00:45:16.790
These men were on a hidden assignment to

00:45:16.800 --> 00:45:19.990
attack Israel. Look how they are

00:45:20.000 --> 00:45:25.750
hiding.

00:45:26.920 --> 00:45:29.510
They were going into Israel to

00:45:29.520 --> 00:45:33.190
attack.

00:45:33.200 --> 00:45:35.070
You see them?

00:45:35.080 --> 00:45:38.310
They're hiding in a trailer bed on a

00:45:38.320 --> 00:45:40.550
semi,

00:45:40.560 --> 00:45:42.230
similar to

00:45:42.240 --> 00:45:44.390
the way I saw the children

00:45:44.400 --> 00:45:50.230
being smuggled in from Mexico.

00:45:50.240 --> 00:45:52.590
This is a semi-trailer bed

00:45:53.560 --> 00:45:56.630
and they're hiding in there.

00:45:56.640 --> 00:46:02.430
That's the driver.

00:46:02.440 --> 00:46:04.150
They don't show the

00:46:04.150 --> 00:46:04.160
whole

00:46:04.160 --> 00:46:06.790
semi; this is just

00:46:06.800 --> 00:46:08.190
the bed of it.

00:46:11.640 --> 00:46:14.590
But at least they caught

00:46:14.590 --> 00:46:14.600
them.

00:46:14.600 --> 00:46:16.070
They didn't have anything

00:46:16.070 --> 00:46:16.080
in

00:46:16.080 --> 00:46:17.590
the load. It would probably have been

00:46:17.600 --> 00:46:19.350
more believable going down the highway

00:46:19.360 --> 00:46:21.590
with some bananas or something in

00:46:21.600 --> 00:46:22.390
it.

00:46:26.120 --> 00:46:27.710
Pretty dumb.

00:46:27.720 --> 00:46:30.270
Next, he indicted that Castro, and then

00:46:31.400 --> 00:46:33.790
NASA.

00:46:35.120 --> 00:46:38.270
Remember I said in

00:46:38.280 --> 00:46:40.750
the days ahead—remember this before

00:46:40.760 --> 00:46:44.550
they even said

00:46:44.550 --> 00:46:44.560
it—I

00:46:44.560 --> 00:46:47.070
put it in the picture

00:46:47.070 --> 00:46:47.080
at

00:46:47.080 --> 00:46:50.150
the beginning of the year. NASA says

00:46:50.160 --> 00:46:52.110
they're going to build the new

00:46:52.120 --> 00:46:56.590
moon base. Tuesday, May 26, is a live

00:46:56.600 --> 00:47:00.270
news event where we'll share updates on

00:47:00.280 --> 00:47:04.790
our lunar exploration plans.

00:47:08.760 --> 00:47:11.587
They want to build a new moon base,

00:47:11.597 --> 00:47:11.630
and

00:47:11.640 --> 00:47:13.750
this is what we're hearing

00:47:13.760 --> 00:47:18.792
today. Go back to the picture.

00:47:19.160 --> 00:47:21.430
I told you this was coming

00:47:21.440 --> 00:47:23.750
at the beginning of the year.

00:47:23.760 --> 00:47:25.070
I said they're going to talk

00:47:25.080 --> 00:47:27.350
about making a moon base and it will be

00:47:27.360 --> 00:47:29.270
in the news a lot.

00:47:29.280 --> 00:47:31.110
Here it is.

00:47:31.120 --> 00:47:33.670
Join us at 2:00 PM on the 26th,

00:47:33.680 --> 00:47:36.990
which is

00:47:37.000 --> 00:47:38.990
next Tuesday.

00:47:49.480 --> 00:47:50.990
I don't always try to

00:47:50.990 --> 00:47:51.000
point

00:47:51.000 --> 00:47:53.830
out that we're accurate,

00:47:53.840 --> 00:47:55.470
that the Lord's accurate, or

00:47:55.470 --> 00:47:55.480
that

00:47:55.480 --> 00:47:57.630
the stuff I'm bringing to you isn't

00:47:57.630 --> 00:47:57.640
flaky

00:47:57.640 --> 00:47:59.870
because there are so many haters,

00:47:59.880 --> 00:48:01.870
but I'm trying to show you this is the

00:48:01.880 --> 00:48:04.030
stuff the Lord's showing us.

00:48:04.040 --> 00:48:06.190
We told you about it clear back here.

00:48:06.200 --> 00:48:08.590
Where's the moon base?

00:48:15.000 --> 00:48:16.910
That's the rocket.

00:48:16.920 --> 00:48:18.990
See, I told Braden to make it next to the rocket. And they did

00:48:18.990 --> 00:48:19.000
it. They put the men in it just like the Lord

00:48:19.000 --> 00:48:20.670
said, and it went around

00:48:20.670 --> 00:48:20.680
the moon. I said

00:48:20.680 --> 00:48:21.710
they're going to

00:48:28.680 --> 00:48:30.390
make a moon base

00:48:32.520 --> 00:48:35.070
right next to it. Do you see that?

00:48:35.080 --> 00:48:36.550
This is what we gave you for

00:48:36.560 --> 00:48:43.830
January. These

00:48:43.830 --> 00:48:43.840
are

00:48:43.840 --> 00:48:45.310
all the things we saw back in

00:48:45.310 --> 00:48:45.320
September,

00:48:45.320 --> 00:48:47.510
October, and November.

00:48:53.680 --> 00:48:55.110
Then I said they were going to

00:48:55.120 --> 00:48:58.270
invade Iran again. Look, that

00:48:58.280 --> 00:49:01.350
was what the bomber was.

00:49:01.360 --> 00:49:02.910
And they did it. Look at the oil

00:49:02.920 --> 00:49:04.870
wells burning. I said the oil wells will

00:49:04.880 --> 00:49:11.710
burn.

00:49:14.160 --> 00:49:21.350
It's all glory to God.

00:49:21.360 --> 00:49:23.430
People

00:49:25.800 --> 00:49:27.670
ask me all

00:49:27.680 --> 00:49:29.190
the time, "Brandon, have you missed

00:49:29.190 --> 00:49:29.200
it before?"Yes, I have.

00:49:29.200 --> 00:49:30.670
I've

00:49:33.360 --> 00:49:34.750
missed it,

00:49:37.160 --> 00:49:39.270
and I'm learning just like everybody

00:49:39.280 --> 00:49:41.870
else. You go through life and you learn

00:49:41.880 --> 00:49:43.830
through trial and

00:49:43.840 --> 00:49:45.150
error.

00:49:45.160 --> 00:49:48.270
Some lessons are harder than others,

00:49:50.440 --> 00:49:52.310
but that's how you learn. When you

00:49:52.320 --> 00:49:54.550
stumble and fall, you pick yourself

00:49:54.560 --> 00:49:58.150
up and keep walking.

00:50:00.200 --> 00:50:02.310
Do you remember the blood

00:50:02.320 --> 00:50:04.830
moons back in 2015? That

00:50:04.840 --> 00:50:07.270
was a time of learning.

00:50:07.280 --> 00:50:08.670
Look at this.

00:50:08.680 --> 00:50:10.390
May

00:50:10.390 --> 00:50:10.400
27.

00:50:10.400 --> 00:50:13.710
This is the new Passion of

00:50:13.720 --> 00:50:16.270
the Christ.

00:50:16.280 --> 00:50:19.670
The Lord said he was going to use

00:50:19.680 --> 00:50:25.590
this film to bring in a great harvest.

00:50:26.880 --> 00:50:28.910
That's exciting.

00:50:28.920 --> 00:50:30.390
This is what we've been praying for. Mel

00:50:30.400 --> 00:50:32.990
Gibson. Is that the Jesus?

00:50:33.000 --> 00:50:34.990
I think so. It looks kind of like

00:50:35.000 --> 00:50:40.070
Jim Caviezel,

00:50:40.070 --> 00:50:40.080
doesn't

00:50:40.080 --> 00:50:42.150
he? I

00:50:42.160 --> 00:50:47.590
hope he's a good Jesus.

00:50:49.880 --> 00:50:52.070
We saw great revivals.

00:50:52.080 --> 00:50:53.070
We were praying for the

00:50:53.080 --> 00:50:54.750
theaters and for Mel Gibson

00:50:54.760 --> 00:50:57.070
to keep accurate with the Word. We

00:50:57.080 --> 00:50:59.910
saw a great revival coming forth out of

00:50:59.920 --> 00:51:04.270
theaters. I saw people stationed

00:51:04.280 --> 00:51:07.070
in theaters who went to

00:51:07.080 --> 00:51:08.990
all of them with tracts

00:51:09.000 --> 00:51:10.950
to witness to the people as they were

00:51:10.960 --> 00:51:13.470
crying. They

00:51:13.480 --> 00:51:15.910
were able to be reached. I saw

00:51:15.920 --> 00:51:18.110
people who spent their whole day there

00:51:18.120 --> 00:51:20.110
handing out tracts to the ones

00:51:20.110 --> 00:51:20.120
who

00:51:20.120 --> 00:51:23.550
needed Jesus.

00:51:23.560 --> 00:51:25.150
Some of the

00:51:25.160 --> 00:51:26.150
theaters didn't say anything because they

00:51:26.160 --> 00:51:27.510
bought a ticket

00:51:27.520 --> 00:51:29.470
and just went out. The

00:51:29.480 --> 00:51:31.630
church stationed people at these

00:51:31.640 --> 00:51:35.190
theaters to bring in the harvest.

00:51:39.200 --> 00:51:42.270
I believe it will be a huge box

00:51:42.280 --> 00:51:44.670
office hit.

00:51:44.680 --> 00:51:46.910
Moving on,

00:51:46.910 --> 00:51:46.920
I

00:51:46.920 --> 00:51:49.110
was praying for

00:51:49.120 --> 00:51:52.990
this pastor in California.

00:51:53.000 --> 00:51:55.470
The Lord showed us a man that God

